            "task_description": "Search for camera in RDR2 equipment compendium. You must FIRST press ESC to open main menu, then navigate Progress > Compendium > Equipment to search for camera. Do NOT move around the map - go directly to the menu system.",
            "sub_task_description_list": [
                "STEP 1: Press ESC to open the main menu immediately - do not walk around",
                "STEP 2: Navigate down to PROGRESS menu option using arrow keys",
                "STEP 3: Press Enter to select PROGRESS",
                "STEP 4: Move right to highlight COMPENDIUM section",
                "STEP 5: Press Enter to select COMPENDIUM",
                "STEP 6: Move right to EQUIPMENT category (from ANIMALS)",
                "STEP 7: Press Enter to select EQUIPMENT category",
                "STEP 8: Use arrow keys to search through the equipment grid for camera",
                "STEP 9: If camera is found, press Enter to view details and log discovery",
                "STEP 10: Press ESC multiple times to exit back to game"
